    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    App
    Main application class for the CSV processor that reads CSV files from S3/COS storage and processes them through Kafka Streams.
    ApplicationConfig
    Immutable configuration holder for the CSV processor application.
    CsvProcessor
    Processor for CSV data with semicolon delimiters and composite key generation.
    EnvironmentUtils
    Utility class for handling environment variables and system properties.
    FileProcessingService
    High-level service that orchestrates the processing of S3 files into Kafka records.
    KafkaStreamsConfigFactory
    Factory class for creating Kafka Streams configuration properties.
    ProcessedRecord
    Immutable representation of a processed CSV record.
    S3ClientFactory
    Factory class for creating AWS S3 client instances.
    S3FileReader
    Service for reading files from S3 or Cloud Object Storage.
    S3Location
    Immutable representation of an S3 or Cloud Object Storage (COS) location.
    StreamsTopologyBuilder
    Builds the Kafka Streams topology for CSV file processing with change detection.
    TimeUtils
    Utility class for date/time operations and JSON timestamp extraction.
